para_trans: Under the aegis of the Water Resources Department
Office of the Superintendent of the Regional Office
Government Circular No: - Seniority - 2024 / Q. 63/2024 Aastha (International)
Date of Office of the Superintendent in the Regional Office under the Water Resources Department
9th January, 2022 to 31st December, 2022, 1st January, 2023 to 31st December, 2022
An interim seniority allowance for the period 2023 has been prepared. It was released on 28 March 2024. All office superintendents have objections to the entry in this seniority list.

They were given 15 days to register. However, since no objections have yet been received from the stakeholders, the final seniority of the office superintendents from the government level has been decided.
The circular is available on the www.maharashtra.gov.in website of the Government of Maharashtra.
